videos.description: Zion Williamson misses a 3-pointer but crashes the boards and finishes with a dunk.
videos.headline: Zion follows up miss with a 2-handed jam

videos.description: Tre Jones comes up with a steal and passes ahead to RJ Barrett who finishes with a slam.
videos.headline: Barrett flushes fast-break dunk

videos.description: Tre Jones goes after a loose ball and runs into Frank Howard, forcing him to exit to the locker room. with a right shoulder injury.
videos.headline: Tre Jones heads to locker room after collision

videos.description: Elijah Hughes cuts to the basket and throws down a powerful dunk.
videos.headline: Hughes back cuts for one-handed dunk

videos.description: Zion Williamson finishes a layup through contact and celebrates with a flex.
videos.headline: Zion flexes after and-1 basket

videos.description: Elijah Hughes heaves a 3/4 court 3-pointer at the buzzer that banks in for Syracuse.
videos.headline: Hughes beats buzzer from opposite free throw line

videos.description: Zion Williamson rejects Oshae Brissett's layup attempt out of bounds.
videos.headline: Zion blocks shot into 1st row

videos.description: Zion Williamson knocks down an open 3-pointer then scores down low in the next possession.
videos.headline: Zion ignites Cameron Indoor with back-to-back baskets

videos.description: Zion Williamson chases down Elijah Hughes and blocks his layup off the backboard.
videos.headline: Zion soars for chasedown block

videos.description: Tyus Battle gets Jack White on his heels and sends him to the ground.
videos.headline: Battle breaks White's ankles

videos.description: Zion Williamson muscles in a basket underneath to give him 34 points which ties the Duke freshman single-game scoring record
videos.headline: Zion ties Duke freshman single-game scoring record

videos.description: Tyus Battle pulls up for a 3-pointer at the buzzer and misses, sending the game into overtime.
videos.headline: Battle misses 3-pointer at buzzer

videos.description: Paschal Chukwu rises up and flushes an alley-oop as Syracuse beats No. 1 Duke in overtime.
videos.headline: Chukwu slams home alley-oop in overtime

videos.description: Tyus Battle credits his Syracuse teammates for being locked in as they pulled off the upset against No. 1 Duke.
videos.headline: Battle: Syracuse 'locked in' to upset No. 1 Duke

videos.description: Zion Williamson goes off for 35 points on 12-of-20 shooting along with 10 rebounds, but Duke falls to Syracuse in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion’s 35 not enough in loss to Syracuse) 2019/01/14 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion's 35 not enough in loss to Syracuse

videos.description: Jim Boeheim throws high praise at Zion Williamson by comparing him to Hall of Famer Charles Barkley, but throws shade at Barkley in the process.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Presser (Boeheim: Zion is like Barkley, but not as fat) 2019/01/14

videos.headline: Boeheim: Zion is like Barkley, but not as fat
